title: Dawn Richard and Spencer Zahn with Magik*Magik Orchestra Live on KEXP

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Dawn Richard and Spencer Zahn with Magik*Magik Orchestra performing live at 25th Street Recording in Oakland, California, during Noise Pop 2025. Recorded February 26, 2025.

Songs:
Moments For Stillness 00:49
Quiet In A World Full Of Noise 04:31
Life In Numbers 08:42
The Dancer 13:24
Traditions 16:44
 
Dawn Richard - Vocals
Spencer Zahn - Bass & Keys
Minna Choi - Conductor
Liana Berube - Violin
Alisa Rose - Violin
Ivo Bokulic - Violin
Kelley Maulbetsch - Cello
Ben Goldberg - Clarinet
Jennifer Ellis - Harp
Dario Slavazza - Sound & Production

Audio Engineer: Kevin Suggs
Guest Audio Engineer: Gabriel Shepard, Karishma Kumar, Collin Purdue
Audio Mixer: Kevin Suggs
Mastering Engineer: Julian Martlew

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen & Luke Knecht
Editor: Jim Beckmann

25th Street Crew:
Gabriel Shepard
Karishma Kumar
Collin Purdue
